<a href="/blog/2013/09/10/this-week-in-spring-september-10-2013-springone2gx-2013-edition">This Week in Spring - September 10, 2013 - SpringOne2GX 2013 Edition</a>
</h2>
<header class="meta-data--container">
<div class="meta-data--item desktop-only">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon engineering"></div>
