<div><p>Welcome to <em>This Week in Spring</em>! <a href="http://springone2gx.com">SpringOne</a> is almost upon us! It kicks off this weekend with the <a href="http://platformcf.com">Cloud Foundry Platform</a> event and continues on until next Thursday. I, personally, am very excited (and a bit nervous!) about this year's show. It's going to be so epic. Yesterday may have been a holiday here in the US (I hope you all enjoyed a wonderful holiday!), but most of us on the Spring team were working fast and furiously in preparation for SpringOne2GX!</p>
